  "_comment": "Per-role suggested-app bundles as winget package IDs. The ninite-personalized module detects the user's role (see role_signals.json), reads which apps are already installed, and outputs a suggested `winget install --id X` list for each bundle that's active. NEVER auto-installs — the module always prints the copy-paste command for the user to run explicitly. Fields per bundle: role, description, apps (array of { id, name, category, optional (bool) }).",
